# Notes:
#   data/raw_openelectricity/ (immutable API responses) IS committed so the whole
#   pipeline replays offline with no API key. The DuckDB warehouse and the
#   consolidated CSV are DERIVED from it and rebuilt in one command, so they are
#   deliberately NOT committed (the .duckdb also exceeds GitHub's 100 MB limit).
